snippet: Tennis star Serena Williams says she is concerned about the Zika outbreak ahead of August's Rio Olympics, but has faith in the support team dealing with worries about the mosquito-carried virus....
lead_paragraph: Tennis star Serena Williams says she is concerned about the Zika outbreak ahead of August's Rio Olympics, but has faith in the support team dealing with worries about the mosquito-carried virus.

headline.print_headline: Serena Concerned Over Zika, but Puts Faith in Olympic Support Team
headline.main: Serena Concerned Over Zika, but Puts Faith in Olympic Support Team
